    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "needs of others in order to fulfill \nyour Life Lesson vibration.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2737880,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "44 AS THE LIFE LESSON: This \nnumber stands for strength\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2742240,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and complete mental control over your \nlife while on earth. It requires\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2746680,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "discipline in every department of life \nso that you may be instrumental in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2750560,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "promoting the material advancement \nof the world. Your mind must be\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2754680,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "trained to let the higher forces work \nwithin it, and you must keep your body\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2759040,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and your environment in order, so that \nyou are ready for any opportunity to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2762880,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "achieve these same results for others. \nYour high energy potential is meant to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2767320,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "further evolution by helping others set \ntheir world in order. You should try\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2772640,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to promote better ethics and justice \nin the world of business. You must\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2776840,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "recognize reality, then use what you \nlearn to alleviate the physical burdens\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2781280,
    "dDurationMs": 5760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of others. You are the instrument by \nwhich this alteration takes place. By\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2787040,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "displaying bravery, resourcefulness, \ncourage and discipline, you serve as an\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2791520,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "example for others. See Edgar \nCayce in Chapter 6 as an example\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2797040,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the 44 vibration.\nThe Soul Number.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2801880,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Soul Number comes from adding \nthe vowels in the name. Always work\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2805800,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with the full name at birth. Prefixes \nand suffixes such as Mr., Mrs., \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2811000,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Jr., Sr., II, III, and Esquire \nare not considered part of \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2815200,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the cosmic name, and are not \nfigured in the total name. \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2819040,
    "dDurationMs": 2680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Place the number value of the \nvowels above the letter in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2821720,
    "dDurationMs": 7280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the name. The vowels are A, E, I, O, \nand U. The letter Y is a vowel when it\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2829000,
    "dDurationMs": 6480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sounds like E, as in the name Mary. It \nis not a vowel in the name May. Y is\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2835480,
    "dDurationMs": 4560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "also a vowel when it is the only vowel \nin the syllable, as in the name Sybil.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2840040,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "W is a vowel when it follows D \nor G as in the names Dwight or\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2843400,
    "dDurationMs": 6280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Gwendolyn, because it carries the vowel sound.\nWe will use our example, Ada Wynn Lunt,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2849680,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "born November 12, 1940. To\narrive at Ada’s Soul Number,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2854320,
    "dDurationMs": 6800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we add the vowels in her name:\n1 + 1 + 7 + 3 equals 12, or 3.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2861120,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Y in Wynn is considered a vowel \nbecause it is the only vowel in the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2865000,
    "dDurationMs": 6920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "name. The 12 is reduced by adding the \n1st digit to the 2nd, or 1 + 2 equals 3.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2871920,
    "dDurationMs": 5680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The number 12 is then written 12/3.\nDiscover your Soul Number by following  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2877600,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the same procedure. Then read\nthe explanation of the basic Soul  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2881560,
    "dDurationMs": 6040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Number (single digit) given below. For a\nfiner delineation of the double digit,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2887600,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "turn to Part 2.\nIn our example, Ada has a Soul  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2891080,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Number of 12 or 3. She would read number\n3 under the Basic Soul Number section  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2895880,
    "dDurationMs": 5600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which follows. She would then turn\nto Part 2 and read the number 12/3  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2901480,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Personal Number Vibration which gives\na deeper look into her real self.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2906800,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Your Soul Number is your real personality, \nthe you that is known only to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2910680,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you. If one embraces the philosophy of \nreincarnation, the Soul Number also\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2915800,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "indicates what you have been in \nprevious lifetimes. This part of your\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2919920,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "personality is not easily recognized \nby others unless they know you very\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2923800,
    "dDurationMs": 6360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "well. The Soul Number is what you, in \nyour inner secret self, desire to be.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2930160,
    "dDurationMs": 3440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This urge may be so strong that it \ncan overcome other vibrations of your\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2933600,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "four basic numbers. Since the \nSoul Number reveals something of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2937240,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "accumulated growth in past lives, it \nbecomes an underlying force which\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2941360,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "influences the actions of your present \nlife. If, however, the soul urge\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2946680,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "remains repressed by outer circumstances, \nand the soul fails to accomplish\n "
