    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2987120,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "contemporaries. If marriage or\npartnership is considered,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2991400,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "investigate the inner yearnings of your\nprospective partner to safeguard  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2995400,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the successful outcome of your\nrelationship. If your individuality  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 2999760,
    "dDurationMs": 5360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is too strong, it could express itself as\nbossiness and be a detriment to personal  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3005120,
    "dDurationMs": 5720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "happiness. So firm is the intensity\nof your focus and so strong the memory  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3010840,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of self-glory from the past that you\nare apt to stand on your convictions even  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3015560,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "though it could disrupt important\nrelationships. Your inner strength  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3019840,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
