    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are a follower rather than a leader. \nTact is a strong point in your makeup;\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3041200,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "therefore, you are a go-between or \nagent, helping to bring peace between\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3045480,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "opposing forces. You avoid hurting the \nfeelings of others to the point of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 3049560,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "subordinating yourself to their wills. \nAs a result, you appear shy and lacking\n "
