      "utf8": "new. They make sense to us, and, for this\nreason, we present them to you.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6082920,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We can best begin by delineating \nthe 4 basic shapes which form a\n "
