      "utf8": "it maintains its shape; and justice,\nbecause it is in a state of perfect  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6111640,
    "dDurationMs": 8960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "balance. A circle contains 360 degrees. \n3 + 6 + 0 is 9. 9 is the highest and final  "
    } ]
