    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "phenomenon we did at age 27. \nThis point roughly corresponds  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6956160,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the 2nd complete Saturn return,\nand brings with it the same choices and  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6960440,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "results we confronted between the\nages of 27 and 29.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6964960,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Here again at 54, for the 2nd \ntime in our life, we come into\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6969080,
    "dDurationMs": 5880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "direct contact with the center triangle \nof spirit, our own true inner self. Will\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6974960,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the inner self express approval of our \npast efforts and reward us with the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6978720,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "fruits of our labor? Or will the inner \nself instead hand us dried dead fruits,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6983920,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "scorched by the burning fire of \ndestruction? Whatever we reap, rest assured\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6989040,
    "dDurationMs": 5640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we have sown. The universal law of \nbalance brings only justice. The law of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6994680,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "physics that for every action there \nis an equal and opposite reaction has\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 6998400,
    "dDurationMs": 5280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "precedence here. It is swift and sure \nand without emotion, pure justice in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7003680,
    "dDurationMs": 7040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "action, but it is the result of our own \npast actions. We are always in control.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7010720,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If we have not sown wisely in the past, \nit is at this point that we can easily\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7015040,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "make the decision to change our \ndirection. The future is ours to create.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7020240,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The wisdom square, which is the \nstructure of the soul, is built upon the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7024320,
    "dDurationMs": 7640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "line assigned the value 5, astrologically \na Mercury number. The ages 54 to 81, \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7031960,
    "dDurationMs": 3400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which the wisdom square \nencompasses, is thus a period\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7035360,
    "dDurationMs": 5360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in life given to much introspection. We \nreflect upon the past, its failures and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7040720,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "accomplishments; the present, at what \nstation in life we find ourselves; and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7045960,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the future, such issues as death \nand the immortality of the soul.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7051360,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In mythology, Mercury was the messenger \nof the deities, the connecting\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7056160,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "communication link between the gods \nof heaven and the mortals on earth.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7060840,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Symbolically, this fleet-footed \nmessenger is the mind, the connection\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7065240,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between soul and body, which, in \nthe period of life between 54 and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7069560,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "81, must now turn from the material \nworld and build the bridge\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7074240,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "between the physical world and the \nworld of Spirit. This is accomplished\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7079160,
    "dDurationMs": 6360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through reflection, reason, order, \nlogic and understanding; all mercurial\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7085520,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "qualities. This bridge between the \nphysical and spiritual will be achieved\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7090440,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through a synthesis of the results \nof the previous processes.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7094680,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In the youth square, mind was formed \nand conditioned and expanded; in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7099320,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the power square, mind had to operate \nin the world of form on its own, as a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7104160,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "single independent entity. Now, in \nthe wisdom square, the mind must\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7109280,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "analyze the results of the soul’s \nevolution through the various stages up to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7112920,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this point and begin to assimilate \nthese findings into the soul’s growth\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7116760,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "experience up to the time the \ntransition process of death occurs.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7120800,
    "dDurationMs": 2960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "For those of us who live through this \nsquare and reach the magic age of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7123760,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "81, there is a three-pronged fork \nat which we must choose a future\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7128160,
    "dDurationMs": 2160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "path.\nWe may decide to leave  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7130320,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the body, at which point we will die and follow\nthe ascending arrow out of the blueprint back to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7135440,
    "dDurationMs": 2360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the source from which we\ncame.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7137800,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Or we may decide to stay in the body, \nwhich implies that we will proceed\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7141640,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in one of 2 directions, depending on \nthe type of seeds we have sown in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7145840,
    "dDurationMs": 6640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the past. Life past 81 is decidedly \nkarmic. If we have wasted our\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7152480,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "life energies and left naught but \ndestruction and unhappiness in our wake,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7156720,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we may very well take the path we \noriginally trod at birth, that first\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7160880,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "horizontal line on the youth square, \nages zero to 9. Because the line\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7165560,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "encompasses childhood we too will \nbecome childlike (senile) and need to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7170640,
    "dDurationMs": 3680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "be cared for like an infant.\nThe 3rd path is for those who  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7174320,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "have sown wisely, who have used the\nprecious God-given life energies  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7178760,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and have honored the body temple in\nservice to the material world through  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7182880,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "understanding, compassion and love\ntowards others. On this sacred path,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7187480,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the few are revered and honored\nbecause their very presence blesses  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7190960,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "those near. Their touch is healing, and\ntheir words express the music of the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7195560,
    "dDurationMs": 6200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spheres, inspiring and lifting the weary\nheart. Blessed are those who tread this path,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7201760,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for theirs is the destiny of\nsupreme devotion to life.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7206160,
    "dDurationMs": 3560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Chapter 4 instructs you in how to \nplace your birth name and birth date\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7209720,
    "dDurationMs": 5640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on the Divine Triangle to work \nwith your personal life blueprint.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7215360,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "FOUR: THE DIVINE TRIANGLE.\nIN THIS CHAPTER, we will explain  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7220480,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how to place your birth name and\nbirth date on the Divine Triangle  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7223720,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and discover the events which you will\nexperience in this lifetime. The Life  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7228520,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Theorem of Pythagoras is the basis of\nthe Divine Triangle, and as you can see  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7232720,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from the blueprint shown earlier, his\nright triangle is the foundation upon  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7236920,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which each of the squares is built.\nThe information that is about to be  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7241040,
    "dDurationMs": 4560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "revealed to you is unique. To our\nknowledge it has never been published  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7245600,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "before. Very likely it was lost in the\ngreat fire that destroyed the fabulous  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7250440,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "library at Alexandria many centuries\nago. Priceless parchments containing the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7255840,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "wisdom of many masters were\nlost.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7259080,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Faith’s teacher learned the method \nfor using this blueprint from the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7262320,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "master KH who, according to some \nsources, was formerly Pythagoras.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7267080,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Perhaps Pythagoras taught this method \nto his disciples. Regardless of one’s\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7271480,
    "dDurationMs": 4560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "belief in such things, the blueprint does \nwork; therefore, in our minds, it is\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7276040,
    "dDurationMs": 5960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "valid. Try it for yourself and see.\nDrawing the Blueprint.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7282000,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The blueprint is set up as follows. \nThe right triangle of Pythagoras\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7286640,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "occupies the center. Squares are built \non each side of the triangle. Each of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7291960,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the 3 lines drawn to complete the \nsquare represents 9 years of life.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7297040,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We begin on line AB at the point of \nentrance indicated by the arrow in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7300680,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "figure 2. The lines represent \nthe ages as follows:\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7304760,
    "dDurationMs": 6280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Line AB: Ages zero to 9\nLine BC: Ages 9 to 18\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7311040,
    "dDurationMs": 6600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Line CD: Ages 18 to 27\nLine DE: Ages 27 to 36\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7317640,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Line EF: Ages 36 to 45\nLine FG: Ages 45 to 54\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7324080,
    "dDurationMs": 6840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Line GH: Ages 54 to 63\nLine HI: Ages 63 to 72\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7330920,
    "dDurationMs": 5600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Line IA: Ages 72 to 81\nOn the figure 2 blueprint, we see  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7336520,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that the youth square covers the ages from \nbirth to 27. The power square covers  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7341320,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the ages 27 to 54. \nThe wisdom square covers  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7345520,
    "dDurationMs": 6400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "ages 54 through 81. After age 81, \nwe begin again on the youth square,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7351920,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but this time on a higher vibration.\nBecome thoroughly acquainted with  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7355840,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the blueprint before proceeding. If\nyou familiarize yourself with it now,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7360520,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the following process will be much\neasier to understand.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7364640,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Labeling the Blueprint.\nThe Birth date: \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7368720,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Using our example, Ada Wynn Lunt, \nwe will place her birth date, \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7373160,
    "dDurationMs": 5280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "November 12, 1940, on the triangle \nin the center of the blueprint.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7378440,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The birth month 11 goes on the vertical \nline AD; the birthdate on the \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7382720,
    "dDurationMs": 6120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "horizontal line DG; and the birth \nyear 1940 on the hypotenuse AG.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7388840,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We reduce the double digits. Here \nthe number 11 becomes 2, the number\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7393440,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "12 becomes 3, and the year 1940 reduces \nto 14 and then 5. If the birth month\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7399880,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and birth date were single digits, such \nas May 4, you would simply place 5\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7404160,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for May on line AD and 4 for the day on line DG.\nThe Name: \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7410600,
    "dDurationMs": 2640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The value of the letters in your \nname is placed on the lines of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7413240,
    "dDurationMs": 5040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the squares. Place the letter \nand its value on each line.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7418280,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In our example, Ada Wynn Lunt, the \nletter of the first name, A, and its\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7422040,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "value, 1, is placed on line \nAB of the youth square.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7425560,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Place the 2nd letter, D, and \nits value, 4, on line BC.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7429720,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Place the 3rd letter of the name, \nA, and its value, 1, on line CD.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7435120,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This completes the youth square, which \nrepresents the ages from birth to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7440480,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you come to the end of your 1st \nname, place an X on that corner,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7444120,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for it marks an important time in your \ndevelopment. Changes will occur, or\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7448880,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a definite event will change your \noutlook in some way. We place an X at\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7453600,
    "dDurationMs": 6040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "point D because we have completed Ada’s 1st name.\nContinue with the power square. Place  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7459640,
    "dDurationMs": 6280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the next letter of the name, in this\ncase W, and its value, 23 or 5, on line DE.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7465920,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Put the following letter, Y, and \nits value, 25 or 7, on line EF.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7471320,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Put the next letter, N, and its \nvalue, 14 or 5, on line FG.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7476320,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This completes the power square, \nwhich represents the ages 27 to 54.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7481480,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "On the wisdom square, place the next \nletter of the name, N, and its value,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 7486160,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
