      "utf8": "individuals who applied for such a\nreading, he brought out information  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12928160,
    "dDurationMs": 6279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on their past lives that was useful in\ntheir present incarnation. In this way he  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12934439,
    "dDurationMs": 3601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "helped thousands of people regain\ntheir health and conduct their  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12938040,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lives in more constructive patterns.\nEdgar Cayce expressed his belief that  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12943560,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the name indicates the soul’s place\nin evolution. He said in reading  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12948000,
    "dDurationMs": 22288,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number 281 dash 31:\n\"Each entity, each soul,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12970288,
    "dDurationMs": 82,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is known in all the experience through its\nactivities - as a name to designate it  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12970370,
    "dDurationMs": 76,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from another, it is not only then a\nmaterial convenience, but it implies...  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12970446,
    "dDurationMs": 63,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a definite period in evolution of\nthe experience of the entity  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12970509,
    "dDurationMs": 2371,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the material plane.\"\nIn reading number 261 dash 15 he says:\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12972880,
    "dDurationMs": 3280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"As related to individuals these \neach vibrate to certain numbers\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12976160,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "according to their name, their \nbirthdate... Then when these appear,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12980120,
    "dDurationMs": 4319,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "they become either as strengths or \nas losses or as helps or as change…\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12984439,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "but... they are rather as the signs, \nor the omens; and may be given as\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12988880,
    "dDurationMs": 3359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "warnings... in any manner that \nthey may be constructive in the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12992239,
    "dDurationMs": 5921,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "experience of the individual.\"\nIn reading number 311 dash 3 he says:\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 12998160,
    "dDurationMs": 5680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "\"In any influence, will... a self, the \nego, the I AM... is the greater force\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13003840,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be dealt with, but as numbers do \ninfluence... a knowledge of same\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13008359,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "certainly gives an individual a \nforesight into relationships...\"\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13012920,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We chose Edgar Cayce to demonstrate \nthe application of double digit\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13016439,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "numerology and the Divine Triangle \nbecause his life clearly demonstrates\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13021160,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the truth of the above quotes. By \ndelineating Edgar Cayce’s name and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
