    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13038439,
    "dDurationMs": 5480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Number 44.\nSoul Number 12 or 3: This is a very  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13043920,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "high spiritual vibration. It represents a\nconscientious individual who is innately  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13048800,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "aware of our spiritual relationship\nto God and who has a great desire to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13053040,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "help others. Through his ideals, Cayce\nwas inspired to dedicate his life to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13057960,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the betterment of humanity. He had a\nheartfelt interest in all who sought his  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13062560,
    "dDurationMs": 5040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "advice, and his greatest desire was to\nhelp them find health and happiness. He  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13067600,
    "dDurationMs": 3200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "taught the value of prayer and\nmeditation and practiced this  "
    } ]
  }, {
