    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13077439,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Outer Personality Number 33: 33 is \na master number which carries an\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13082319,
    "dDurationMs": 4761,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "almost Christ-like vibration. In his \nouter physical life, Cayce worked\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13087080,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "constantly, giving both diagnostic \nand life readings through which he\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13090960,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "brought out the theory of reincarnation, \nand revealed knowledge of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13094600,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "astrology and numbers as related \nto the lives of human beings. He\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13099239,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "interpreted the Bible as well. Because \nhe was seen by many as a savior, he\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13104479,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "felt the need and obligation to work \nfor the good of others, even though his\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13108760,
    "dDurationMs": 8320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "own fortunes would suffer.\nPath of Destiny Number 45 or 9:  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13117080,
    "dDurationMs": 4359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This number indicates that his mission in\nlife was highly spiritual and mystical.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13121439,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "He was not satisfied with worldly\nsuccess alone. This Path of Destiny  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13125920,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Number signifies one who loves to\nteach and serve others. It endowed  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13129760,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Cayce with the courage and fortitude to\nface the changes and emergencies in his  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13134160,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "life, giving him faith that\neverything would work out with  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13137080,
    "dDurationMs": 5119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "God’s help and guidance. This number also\nindicates one who is willing to work hard,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13142199,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "even at the expense of his own\nhealth. Cayce’s theme seemed to be:  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13146760,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "“Let me ever be a channel of blessings,\ntoday, now, to those I contact in every way.”\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13152160,
    "dDurationMs": 5079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Life Lesson Number 44: This \nnumber, derived from the birthdate,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13157239,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "indicates what a person should learn \nin this life. This master number 44 is\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13162120,
    "dDurationMs": 5079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "called Atlas. In mythology Atlas \nsupports the heavens on his shoulders. \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13167199,
    "dDurationMs": 4601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In other words, Cayce would take\nresponsibility for others, attend  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13171800,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "faithfully to duty and make the best of any\nsituation which had to be met. He possessed  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13176960,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "common sense and foresight in\norder to make fair judgments. He  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13181040,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was very understanding in his dealings\nwith others, anxious to please and  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13184840,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "help in any possible way. He believed\nthat service was the way toward mastership,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13190080,
    "dDurationMs": 2920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and his life and works are\nample proof of this.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13193000,
    "dDurationMs": 3399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "To choose which numbers are important \nin the delineation of events in a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13196399,
    "dDurationMs": 5440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lifetime, select those that coincide \nwith the four personal numbers (in our\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13201840,
    "dDurationMs": 8600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "example, 12 or 3, 33, 45 or 9 and 44). \nThe personal numbers are activated\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13210439,
    "dDurationMs": 5360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "whenever they are energized by \ncorresponding numbers. Thus a 12 or 3 event\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13215800,
    "dDurationMs": 5360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would energize Cayce’s 12 or 3 Soul \nNumber, as would any type of 3; a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13221160,
    "dDurationMs": 9039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "single 3, a 21, a 30, a 39, etc. \nTherefore any variation of 3, 6, 8 or 9\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13230199,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "would activate the corresponding \npersonal number; however, it would\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13234279,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "activate it according to the double digit \nvariation. In addition, it seems that\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13239279,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "often one’s master numbers, e.g. Cayce’s \n33 and 44, are triggered by any of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13244680,
    "dDurationMs": 11400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the four master numbers: 11, 22, 33, 44 \nor by their base digits 2, 4, 6 and 8.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13256080,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "To see how Cayce’s life is reflected \nin his numerological blueprint, we\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13260520,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "examine each nine-year cycle in two \nways. First, we will look at the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13265399,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "correlations between events in his life \nand the experiences under the major\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13269680,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "process and the minor process which \nare operating during each nine-year\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13273680,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "cycle. Secondly, we can see whether \nany of the events correspond with the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13278600,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "personal year and the three four-month \nperiod numbers also operating\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13282439,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "during that time.\nWe will discuss here only the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13286680,
    "dDurationMs": 5760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "most significant events of Cayce’s life. We\nwill, however, list all the experiences under  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13292439,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the major and minor process for\neach nine-year cycle; in addition  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13297000,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we will list each personal year and that\nyear’s division into the three four-month  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13300800,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "periods. You will then have before\nyou all the temporary numbers which  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13305479,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "affected Cayce throughout his life,\neven though we will discuss here only the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13310319,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "most significant events of his\nlife.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13313439,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Age: Birth to Nine. To calculate the \nexperiences of Edgar Cayce’s first\n "
