  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13332920,
    "dDurationMs": 9359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "end of line AB, 0 and 9. 0 + 1 is 1. 9 \nminus 1 is 8. At ages 1 and 8, Cayce had a\n "
