  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13342279,
    "dDurationMs": 8841,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "19 or 1 experience. 0 + 3 is 3. 9 minus \n3 is 6. At ages 3 and 6, Cayce had a 3\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13351120,
    "dDurationMs": 8119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "experience. 0 + 8 is 8. 9 minus 8 is \n1. At ages 8 and 1, Cayce had a 44\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13359239,
    "dDurationMs": 2761,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "experience.\nTo calculate the experiences  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13362000,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "by the minor process, we work with the\nnumbers in the center of the square,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13365720,
    "dDurationMs": 7240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "19 or 1, on the side of the triangle, 3, and\non the first line, 5, and the ages at either  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13372960,
    "dDurationMs": 9720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "end of line AB. 0 + 5 is 5. 5 + 3 is\n8. At age 5, Cayce had an 8 experience.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13382680,
    "dDurationMs": 8800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "9 minus 5 is 4. 5 + 19 is 24 or 6. At \nage 4, Cayce had a 24 or 6 experience.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13391479,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "We do not have much information about \nCayce’s first nine years. We do\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13396040,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "know that, according to his mother, \neven as a small child he saw and talked\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13400880,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with invisible playmates. At age four \nthe death of a much loved grandfather\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13405800,
    "dDurationMs": 4399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "proved to be a very emotional experience. \nA few months later he claimed\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13410199,
    "dDurationMs": 3761,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that his grandfather appeared and \ntalked with him. This occurred under a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13413960,
    "dDurationMs": 6239,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "minor process 24 or 6 experience, a love \nand family vibration. On the period\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13420199,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "table, at age four all basic \nnumbers are energized.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13424359,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Here are the calculations for the \nyearly periods from birth to nine.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13428800,
    "dDurationMs": 5040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ages Nine to Eighteen: To calculate \nthe experiences of these years by the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13433840,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "major process, we work with the number \nin the center of the square, 19 or 1,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13439920,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the number on the side of the triangle, \n3, and the number in the center of the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13444439,
    "dDurationMs": 11681,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "triangle, 44, and the age at each end of line BC, \n9 and 18. 9 + 1 is 10. 18 minus 1 is 17. At ages  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13456120,
    "dDurationMs": 11079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "10 and 17, Cayce had a 19 or 1 experience. 9 + 3 \nis 12. 18 minus 3 is 15. At ages 12 and 15, Cayce  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13467199,
    "dDurationMs": 10641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "had a 3 experience. 9 + 8 is 17. 18 minus 8 is \n10. At ages 10 and 17, Cayce had a 44 experience.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13477840,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "To calculate the experiences by the \nminor process, we work with the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13481680,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number in the center of the square, 19 \nor 1, the number on the side of the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13486439,
    "dDurationMs": 7320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "triangle, 3, the number on the line, 4, \nand the ages on each end of line BC, 9\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13493760,
    "dDurationMs": 10000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and 18. 9 + 4 is 13. 4 + 19 is 23 or 5. At \nage 13, Cayce had a 23 or 5 experience.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13503760,
    "dDurationMs": 8360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "18 minus 4 is 14. 4 + 3 is 7. At \nage 14, Cayce had a 7 experience.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13512120,
    "dDurationMs": 6359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At age 10, in a 45 or 9 personal year, \nCayce began work as a church sexton.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13518479,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This year corresponds to his Path \nof Destiny Number, 45 or 9, and the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13522760,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "experiences of this particular time \nwere indicative of his future path.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13527640,
    "dDurationMs": 3560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At the age of 12 or 13, Cayce was \nplaying in one of his favorite\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13531199,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spots by a brook. He sat down to read \nthe Bible which he always kept with\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13535439,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "him. He turned to the Book of \nJudges (13, verses 2 through 22) \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13540319,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to read about the vision of Manoah and, \nwhile perusing the passage,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13544399,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "he heard a strange sound, saw a\nbright light, and then heard a  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13548520,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "voice saying, “Your prayers have been heard; \nwhat would you ask that I may grant your wish?”\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13554960,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Cayce answered: “Just that I may be \nhelpful to others, especially children\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13559680,
    "dDurationMs": 6040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who are ill, and that I may love my fellow man.”\nThe next day, he could not keep his mind  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13565720,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "on his school work. Because\nhis spelling was unsatisfactory,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13569520,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "his teacher made him stay after school and\nwrite a misspelled word on the blackboard  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13573239,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "five-hundred times. That night\nhis father decided to drill him on  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13578359,
    "dDurationMs": 5480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the spelling homework, but Cayce did not\ndo well. It was late and he was getting  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13583840,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sleepy. Just then Edgar seemed to\nhear a voice within him saying:  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13589080,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "“Sleep a little and we may help you.”\nHe laid his head on the spelling book and  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13594080,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "slept for a few minutes. When\nhe awoke he knew how to spell  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13598080,
    "dDurationMs": 6760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "every word in the entire book. This is his\nstory of how universal consciousness came to him.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13605479,
    "dDurationMs": 5440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A few days later he was hit by a \nbaseball. He returned home, dazed, and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13610920,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "asked his mother to make a certain \npoultice for the back of his head. She\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13614840,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "did, and in the morning he was well. \nThis was his first insight into\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13619600,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "successful health prescriptions.\nDuring these two years, his basic  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13623720,
    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Soul Number, 12 or 3, was being\nactivated. At age 12, he had a  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13628680,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "major-process 3 experience on the\nblueprint, and at age 13, he was  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13633399,
    "dDurationMs": 6681,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a 39 or 3 personal year. During that\n39 or 3 personal year, he experienced a 12  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13640080,
    "dDurationMs": 3079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or 3 period number between\nNovember and March, which  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13643159,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "energized again his Soul Number, and \nillustrated graphically how his inner  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13647600,
    "dDurationMs": 5960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "talents and abilities from past lifetimes\nwere being filtered into his consciousness.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13653560,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At age fifteen Cayce quit school \nand went to work on a farm. At this\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13658319,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "time, he was also under a major-process \n3 experience on the blueprint,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13662399,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which showed that his latent talents \nwere being awakened. Perhaps a formal\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13666600,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "education would have disturbed his \ngrowing psychic talents. Also on the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13670680,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "period table this occurred under a 17 \nor 8 four-month period. This relates to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13675840,
    "dDurationMs": 7600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "his Life Lesson Number, 44. Basically \nthe 8 (a master number, 44, reduced)\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13683439,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "means that the serious business of the \nLife Lesson is being energized. 8 is a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13688520,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "disciplinary number, and it means \nthat work and responsibility are now\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13692720,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "necessary for accomplishment.\nHere are the calculations for the  "
    } ]
  }, {
