    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13778800,
    "dDurationMs": 9760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "27 minus 7 is 20. 7 + 19 is 26 or 8. At \nage 20 Cayce had a 26 or 8 experience.\n "
