    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13818199,
    "dDurationMs": 4801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as revealed in later readings which \ndepicted their past incarnations together.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13823000,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It was destined for both of them to \nwork out their former lives in their\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13826720,
    "dDurationMs": 3400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "present relationship.\nHere are the calculations  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13830120,
    "dDurationMs": 7079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for the yearly periods, ages 18 to 27 \nwhich reflect that portion of Cayce’s life.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13837199,
    "dDurationMs": 4801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When Cayce was 22, he obtained \na job as a traveling salesman.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13842000,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This was during a 12 or 3 period. \nAfter some months he became ill and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13847000,
    "dDurationMs": 4319,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "decided to return to Hopkinsville. He \nwas unable to speak above a whisper,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13851319,
    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the story goes, and a traveling \nhypnotist, hearing of the case, suggested\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13856279,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "using hypnotism to determine the \ncause of the ailment. Cayce underwent\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13861359,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "hypnosis easily, and talked naturally \nwhile under its influence. He described\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13866600,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "his own condition as a partial \nparalysis of the vocal cords and also\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13870760,
    "dDurationMs": 5439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "prescribed the cure. He said, “The body \nshould increase circulation to the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13876199,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "affected part for a short time.”\nTo everyone’s surprise, his throat  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13880920,
    "dDurationMs": 6279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "turned red, then redder, until Cayce\nsaid in a clear voice: “Suggest that the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13887199,
    "dDurationMs": 4641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "circulation return to normal and the\nbody awaken.”\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13891840,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This was a turning point in a technique \nthat he was to develop and use\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13895479,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "countless times to help others. \nHe was now 24 years old. He was\n "
    } ]
  }, {
