    "dDurationMs": 4399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to his Life Lesson Number, 44.\nHe moved to Bowling Green,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13916239,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Kentucky, at age 25, and took a\nposition in a bookstore. Stories of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13921159,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "his strange gift were spreading. At this\ntime in his life he was asked to give a  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13925640,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "reading for a school superintendent’s\nfive-year-old daughter. Her mind had  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13929600,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "stopped developing and she suffered\nvarious other ailments. Many doctors  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13933960,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "had been consulted but none could\nfind a way to help the child. Cayce  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13938840,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "agreed to give a reading, and, while in\ntrance, he related the cause and prescribed  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13943840,
    "dDurationMs": 3680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the treatment for the ailment. He\nfound that the child had struck  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13947520,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "her spine when she stepped down from a\ncarriage. This had caused an impingement  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 13951920,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
