      "utf8": "process, we work with the number in \nthe center of the square, 35 or 8; the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14922239,
    "dDurationMs": 4801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number on the side of the triangle, 23 \nor 5; the number in the center of the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14927040,
    "dDurationMs": 9199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "triangle, 44; and the age at each end \nof line HI, 63 and 72. 63 + 8 is 71.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14936239,
    "dDurationMs": 9280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "72 minus 8 is 64. At age 64 (and 71, had \nhe not died) he had a 35 or 8 experience. \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14945520,
    "dDurationMs": 6120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "63 + 5\nis 68. 72 minus 5 is 67. At  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14951640,
    "dDurationMs": 12479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "age 67 (and 68, had he not died) he had a 23 or 5\nexperience. 63 + 8 is 71. 72 minus 8 is 64. At age  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14964119,
    "dDurationMs": 5761,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "64 (and 71 had he not died) he\nhad a 44 experience.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14969880,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "To calculate the experiences by the \nminor process, we work with the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14973600,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number in the center of the square, 35 \nor 8; the number on the side of the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14978720,
    "dDurationMs": 6880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "triangle, 23 or 5; the number on line \nHI, 7; and the ages on each end of line\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14985600,
    "dDurationMs": 9760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "HI, 63 and 72. 63 + 7 is 70. 7 + 23 is \n30 or 3. At age 70 Cayce would have had\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 14995359,
    "dDurationMs": 8240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a 30 or 3 experience. 72 minus \n7 is 65. 7 + 35 is 42 or 6. \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15003600,
    "dDurationMs": 6240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "At age 65, Cayce had a 42 or 6 experience.\nAccording to the major process calculations,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15009840,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Cayce’s basic number 8 (44\nreduced) is activated twice,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15014520,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "indicating that this was a time for him to\nexperience his Life Lesson. At age 65  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15019840,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the Search for God books became\navailable. These books are still  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15023600,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "used by all Association's study groups \nboth in the United States and abroad.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15028720,
    "dDurationMs": 6439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Here are the calculations for the yearly periods, \nages 63 to 67, which relate to the experiences  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15035159,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of Cayce’s life mentioned above.\nA personal year runs from birthdate  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15039439,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to birthdate; thus Cayce was still in\nhis 1944 year when he died. The actual  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15045520,
    "dDurationMs": 5760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "death date was January 3, 1945, a\n23 or 5 experience.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15051279,
    "dDurationMs": 6721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Cayce’s last reading was given September \n17, 1944, during a 26 or 8 period.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15058000,
    "dDurationMs": 6000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "On January 3, 1945, Cayce’s work in \nthe physical body was completed. He\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15064000,
    "dDurationMs": 6159,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "died at 67 years and 10 months of age, \nin a 39 or 3 personal year and a 21 or 3\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15070159,
    "dDurationMs": 3601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "period number, which shows that the \ntransition occurred under his Soul\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15073760,
    "dDurationMs": 4479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Number, 12 or 3.\nEven after his death, Cayce’s  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15078239,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "influence is still felt by many. Some of his\npredictions have been fulfilled; some have not  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15083640,
    "dDurationMs": 6320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "yet occurred. The Association for Research and \nEnlightenment continues to thrive and in 1956  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15089960,
    "dDurationMs": 5159,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was able to buy back the old hospital building \nin Virginia Beach. This is now the location of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15095119,
    "dDurationMs": 8120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the headquarters and it is open to the public. \nIn 1975 a beautiful new library was opened,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15103239,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "dedicated to the work of the Association. \nWithin its doors can be found all the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15108119,
    "dDurationMs": 5040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "information from Cayce’s readings, \nsorted and filed in encyclopedic form,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15113159,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "thus making available the vast \ninformation which came through the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15116159,
    "dDurationMs": 9160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "instrumentality of one man: Edgar Cayce.\nSEVEN: BIBLE SYMBOLOGY.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15125319,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "THE BIBLE is a veritable mine of \nnumber symbology. Both the Old\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15129760,
    "dDurationMs": 3640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and New Testaments reveal, by \nuse of numbers, depth of meaning\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15133399,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and hidden concepts which commonly \nescape the casual reader.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15137239,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Zohar, a collection of mystical \nkabbalistic writings, states that, The\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15141960,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Universe was created by 3 forms of \nexpression - Numbers, Letters and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15147040,
    "dDurationMs": 5840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Words. The letters in all alphabets \nrepresent definite powers. To study the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15152880,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vibratory value of numbers and letters \nis to study the divine creative\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15156720,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "energies in various degrees of \nmanifestation. Every name in the Bible\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15161239,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "describes a deeper meaning regarding \nthe person or place to which it\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15164359,
    "dDurationMs": 5840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "applies. Similarly certain words are \nmade to have hidden significance.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15170199,
    "dDurationMs": 2360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Old Testament.\nTo read through the Old  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15172560,
    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Testament, the Torah, Kabbalah, and other\nsacred Hebraic writings is to become well  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15177520,
    "dDurationMs": 2840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "aware of how the Hebrews used\nthe science of names and numbers  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15180359,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in their number-letter code. By this code\nthey wished to obscure their meanings from  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15185080,
    "dDurationMs": 3199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the uninitiate, and at the same\ntime to reveal their inner  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15188279,
    "dDurationMs": 3360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "teachings to the initiate.\nEach letter of the Hebrew  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15191640,
    "dDurationMs": 5560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "alphabet has several meanings - for example\nthe letter Aleph (A) means life breath,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15197199,
    "dDurationMs": 6200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "power, source; while the letter Beth\n(B) means house, shelter; and so on  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15203399,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with every letter. The symbology\nallowed hidden teachings to be  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15207199,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "evident to those who knew how to read the\ndeeper message contained in the names of all  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15211239,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "persons and places described.\nScholars could also penetrate  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15215560,
    "dDurationMs": 5720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the mask of allegory and receive or give\ndivine guidance through numbers and letters.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15221279,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "For example, the story of Cain slaying \nAbel is about fraternal rivalry. But\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15226479,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symbolically, the name Cain means \nbody and materialistic human desires,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15230920,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "while Abel stands for the soul and \nidealistic human nature. These characters\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15235640,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "were so named to warn that materialism \nwould kill spiritual ideas; hence\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15240640,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Cain was said to have killed \nAbel (Genesis 4 verse 8).\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15244760,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Many biblical characters who reached \nperiods of spiritual growth and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15247880,
    "dDurationMs": 5479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "development in their lives were given \nnew names by divine direction. Thus\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15253359,
    "dDurationMs": 5721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Abram became Abraham (Genesis 17 verse \n5) and Sara became Sarah (Genesis\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15259080,
    "dDurationMs": 6760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "17 verse 15). In both cases, the Hebrew \nHeh (H), a letter meaning light and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15265840,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "having a vibration of 9, was added to \nthe name to denote the attainment of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15270040,
    "dDurationMs": 3239,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spiritual light.\nNew Testament writers also  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15273279,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "made name changes to point out an\nindividual’s spiritual progress.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15277319,
    "dDurationMs": 6960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "For example, Saul became Paul after his\nconversion to Christianity (Acts 9 verses 1 to 22,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15284279,
    "dDurationMs": 2960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and 13 verse 9). \nThis symbolized the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15287239,
    "dDurationMs": 4841,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "removal of the Hebrew Shin (S) and \nits replacement with the Hebrew Peh\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15292080,
    "dDurationMs": 6239,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "(P). Shin means tooth or fang of a \nserpent. Peh means mouth. After this\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15298319,
    "dDurationMs": 6280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "change, Saul became Paul, the spokesman \nfor Christ (Acts 13 verse 9). As\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15304600,
    "dDurationMs": 6360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Proverbs 22 verse 1 states, a good name \nis rather to be chosen than great riches.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15310960,
    "dDurationMs": 3040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A further use of numbers in biblical \nlanguage involves recounting the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15314000,
    "dDurationMs": 5319,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number of years a person lived, begat \nand died. These numbers did not refer\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15319319,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the person’s age in years, but rather \nto progress in spiritual attainment.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15324520,
    "dDurationMs": 3521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The meaning of the name of the begotten \nindicated the development of a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15328040,
    "dDurationMs": 5800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "characteristic. Cycles also were indicated \nby the generations of descent. For\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15333840,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "example, from Adam to Noah there \nwere 9 generations, and from Noah\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15338119,
    "dDurationMs": 4601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to Abraham there were also 9 \ngenerations. That made Noah the ninth\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15342720,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from Adam, and Abraham the ninth from Noah.\nAdam had three sons—Cain (body),  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15348800,
    "dDurationMs": 5399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Abel (soul) and Seth (replacement\nfor Abel to carry the spiritual light). In  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15354199,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a parallel situation, Noah also had\nthree sons: Shem (spirit),  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15358640,
    "dDurationMs": 5880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ham (physical nature) and Japhet (mental\nnature). These names represented the growth  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15364520,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of humanity in consciousness\nafter 18 cycles of change.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15368560,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Abram meant father, while Abraham \nimplied the added faith in God\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15372279,
    "dDurationMs": 4681,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which he had come to realize. At \n99 years of age, Abraham begat\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15376960,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Isaac, whose name meant joy in divine \nsonship. Isaac begat Jacob, whose \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15381880,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "name meant illumination through \nunfolding soul. Jacob’s 12 sons\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15386640,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "(Genesis 35 verses 22 to 27) refer to the twelve \ntypes of consciousness represented by the 12  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15393080,
    "dDurationMs": 5359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "character types in the signs of the zodiac.\nTo study the whole Bible in this light  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15398439,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is to have a lifetime of fascinating\ndiscovery. It can be said that Hebrew,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15403520,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "more than any other language, offers\nus a great opportunity to study the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15407359,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "profound power and significance of\nnames. Here is a short list of keywords  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15412199,
    "dDurationMs": 6801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for the numbers in biblical times:\n0. Source before manifestation.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15419000,
    "dDurationMs": 7479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "1. God, the one immutable divine unity.\n2. Duality; human, not divine.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15426479,
    "dDurationMs": 6000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "3. Attributes of 1 + 2 equals 3; \nunion of divine and human qualities.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15432479,
    "dDurationMs": 7400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "4. The idea of solidity—steadfastness.\n5. Humanity with its five developed senses.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15439880,
    "dDurationMs": 8359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "6. Equilibrium, fitness, peace.\n7. Humanity’s septenary nature, cyclic fullness.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15448239,
    "dDurationMs": 8320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "8. Accumulation, strength, power, augmentation.\n9. Consolidation, conservation, humaneness. \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15456560,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "(The true mission of the 9 is to \nserve as a minister of God on earth.)\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15460720,
    "dDurationMs": 6280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "10. God and humanity, \nfather-mother-deity, completion.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15467000,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Modern numerology has grown partly \nfrom these concepts. The numbers\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15470800,
    "dDurationMs": 3280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and letters reflect meanings from \nthe past coupled with many added\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15474080,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spiritual interpretations. Meanings \nof our names today have deep\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15477960,
    "dDurationMs": 3680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "significance and can be delineated \nletter by letter and number by number as\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15481640,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we attain cycles of expression year by \nyear in our own lives. These are fully\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15486239,
    "dDurationMs": 6721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "explained in earlier chapters of this book.\n0. GENESIS, which means “first cause,” relates  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15492960,
    "dDurationMs": 2880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the primordial source.\nThe first few verses of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15495840,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Genesis pertain only to the one God, as divine\ncreator, who brings the world into existence out  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15501000,
    "dDurationMs": 3279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the void, or from the\nunmanifest.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15504279,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "1. LET THERE BE LIGHT (Genesis \n1 verse 3). The first spiritual\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15509399,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "emanation was light. If our soul \ncontinues to follow the light, we will\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15513760,
    "dDurationMs": 6200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "get back to our source. 1 stands for \na beginning, a new start and unity.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15519960,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "2. AND GOD DIVIDED the light from \nthe darkness (Genesis 1 verse 4).\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15525479,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In 2 there is duality, day and night, \nheaven and earth, man and woman\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15530199,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and all pairs of opposites. Thus the \ndevelopment of choice began between\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15534680,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "good and evil, true and false \nand positive and negative.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15539279,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Pythagoras says: 2 is the imperfect \ncondition into which being falls,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15543680,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when it becomes detached from the \nmonad, God. Manly Hall in The\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15548840,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Mystical Christ, states: When the eyes \nof the both are opened, the sight of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15553119,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the soul is obscured.\n3. THE FIRST TRINITY;  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15558119,
    "dDurationMs": 6400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Adam and Eve and child. Thus 3 means\nmanifestation and expansion. Other trinities  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15564520,
    "dDurationMs": 3120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "survive in our world - \nbody, soul, and spirit,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15567640,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the 3 divisions of mind—conscious,\nsubconscious and super-conscious.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15572279,
    "dDurationMs": 3801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "4. MANY BIBLICAL REFERENCES are \ntaken from the cycles of the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15576080,
    "dDurationMs": 4319,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "natural world. The symbology of \nthe four seasons and four winds is\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15580399,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "embodied in Ezekiel’s vision of the \n4 living creatures: the face of a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15584680,
    "dDurationMs": 5600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "man, the face of a lion, the face of an \nox and the face of an eagle (Ezekiel\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15590279,
    "dDurationMs": 6280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "1 verses 5 to 14). These four relate \nto the four fixed signs of the zodiac.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15596560,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The four elements appear symbolically \nas the birds of the air, the fish of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15600720,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the sea, the fire of the Lord and \nthe products of the earth. Genesis  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15605640,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "2 verses 10 to 14 tells of the river out of \nEden which parted into 4 heads. The rivers\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15611720,
    "dDurationMs": 5720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "were named Pison, Gihon, Hiddekel \nand Euphrates. Metaphysically these\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15617439,
    "dDurationMs": 6800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "names mean spirit (fire), breath (air), \nbody (earth) and blood (water). These\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15624239,
    "dDurationMs": 3801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symbolize spirit, mind, body and \nsoul which are the 4 principles that\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15628040,
    "dDurationMs": 7079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vitalize the material body during the earth life.\n5. METAPHYSICALLY a river represents  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15635119,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vital force. Human beings\nare the container of this force,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15639439,
    "dDurationMs": 5601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as a garden symbolizes the body. The\nriver of Genesis 2 verses 10 to 14,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15645040,
    "dDurationMs": 2960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "described under number 4, \nrepresents the flow of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15648000,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "humanity itself throughout the earth, \nwhich divides and divides until it\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15652680,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "covers all the earth. The 5 is the \nnumber of humanity with our five\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15657279,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "developed senses. The five senses are \nintroduced in the early chapters of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15662000,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Genesis to indicate that the senses \nare essential in human creation; and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15666720,
    "dDurationMs": 3479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "therefore 5 is the number of humanity.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15670199,
    "dDurationMs": 3440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Five plays an important part in the \nstory of David and Goliath: and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15673640,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "David chose five smooth stones out of \nthe brook” and David took a stone \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15678000,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and smote the Philistine Goliath in \nthe forehead. The stone sunk into the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15682279,
    "dDurationMs": 5480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "forehead and he fell to the ground, \n(First Samuel 17 verse 40). The 5 stones\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15687760,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "represent the spiritualization of \nDavid’s senses. David believed in the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15692439,
    "dDurationMs": 3680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "indwelling God of love and had learned \nto depend upon the spiritual power\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15696119,
    "dDurationMs": 4601,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "within himself. According to a mystical \nlegend, when David touched the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15700720,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "five stones they became as one stone, \nthus combining the total powers of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15704920,
    "dDurationMs": 5800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "his senses. The name Goliath means \nmaterial power; thus the story is meant\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15710720,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to demonstrate the power of the \nspiritual over the material.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15714920,
    "dDurationMs": 4399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "6. THE PREPARATIONS for the \nemergence of humanity had all been\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15719319,
    "dDurationMs": 4761,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "made during the 5 days of creation, \nso on the sixth day, God made\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15724080,
    "dDurationMs": 5079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "human beings. In the image of God \ncreated He him, male and female\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15729159,
    "dDurationMs": 6440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "created He them (Genesis 1 verse 27). \nSo 6 is associated with generation,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15735600,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "motherhood, fatherhood, domesticity \nand service. Home, family and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15741680,
    "dDurationMs": 5840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "children are the concerns of 6; \nhuman relationships and love abound.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15747520,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Moses, the first lawgiver, patterned \nthe Ten Commandments after the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15751119,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Lord’s example of creating the \nuniverse in 6 days. 6 days shalt thou\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15756000,
    "dDurationMs": 6040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "labor and do all thy work (Exodus 20 \nverse 9). Therefore 6 is related to labor\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15762040,
    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and service, as shown by the \nsixth sign of the zodiac, Virgo.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15767000,
    "dDurationMs": 3080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Through love, the sixth sense is to \nbe developed as people demonstrate\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15770080,
    "dDurationMs": 5079,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "their godliness. The Book of Ruth is \nkeyed to the number 6 and to love. In\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15775159,
    "dDurationMs": 5280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Ruth 3 verse 15, Boaz gives Ruth 6 \nmeasures of barley, symbolic of love and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15780439,
    "dDurationMs": 3641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "protection.\n7. IS THE PRINCIPLE NUMBER  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15784080,
    "dDurationMs": 6279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the Bible; it is used innumerable\ntimes (some say over 360) throughout  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15790359,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "both Old and New Testaments. \nBut the seventh day is the Sabbath  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15794640,
    "dDurationMs": 2960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the Lord thy God... \nFor in six days the Lord  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15797600,
    "dDurationMs": 4440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "made heaven and earth... and rested the\nseventh day; wherefore the Lord blessed the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15802040,
    "dDurationMs": 4359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "seventh day and hallowed it\n(Exodus 20:10-11).\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15806399,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "One of the most profound examples \nof the use of the symbolic number 7\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15810239,
    "dDurationMs": 5521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is related to the fall of Jericho in \nthe Book of Joshua, 6 verses 1 to 20:\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15815760,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And the Lord said unto Joshua: And \nye shall compass the city... and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15820040,
    "dDurationMs": 5680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "go round about the city once. Thus \nshalt thou do six days... And the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15825720,
    "dDurationMs": 3880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "priests shall bear before the ark \nseven trumpets of rams’ horns: and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15829600,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the seventh day ye shall compass the \ncity seven times, and the priests \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15833319,
    "dDurationMs": 3521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "shall blow with the trumpets. When \nthey make a long blast with the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15836840,
    "dDurationMs": 3479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "ram’s horn and when ye hear the \nsound of the trumpet, all the people\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15840319,
    "dDurationMs": 3721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "shall shout with a great shout, and \nthe wall of the city shall fall down\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15844040,
    "dDurationMs": 2720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "flat.\nIt becomes evident that the fall  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15846760,
    "dDurationMs": 5880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of Jericho was not by warfare but rather\nwas by the principle of the 7. Victory  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15852640,
    "dDurationMs": 4120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was achieved by means of the positive\nvibration of sound which had been built  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15856760,
    "dDurationMs": 7600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "up to a tremendous power.\n8. THE MYSTERY of the 8 is  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15864359,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that of eternal and continuous spiral\nmotion, which is constant throughout  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15868760,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the universe. The life force\ncurrents sweep through the body in  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15873000,
    "dDurationMs": 4399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the form of a figure 8, following the\ncerebro-spinal and the sympathetic  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15877399,
    "dDurationMs": 6360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "nervous systems, like radiations of light.\nThis is why in deep meditation one sees a real  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15883760,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "light within. The infinity symbol,\nthe horizontal 8, means as above,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15889080,
    "dDurationMs": 6880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so below. It is a symbol of power. In\nGenesis 17 verse 10 the rite and covenant  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15895960,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of circumcision was to be performed on\nthe eighth day of a man child’s life.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15900640,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This was considered one of the most\nimportant covenants between God and humanity.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15905640,
    "dDurationMs": 5200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "9. IS THE ULTIMATE, containing the \nforces of all the other numbers. It\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15910840,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "stands for a complete cycle of \ngrowth. The nine generations from\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15915359,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Adam to Noah and from Noah to Abraham \nindicate stages of growth and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15919119,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "development. Noah was the ninth from \nAdam, and Abraham was the ninth\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15924000,
    "dDurationMs": 2560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from Noah.\nWhen Abram received  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15926560,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "his covenant from God and his new name,\nAbraham, he was ninety and nine years  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15931159,
    "dDurationMs": 7200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "old (Genesis 17 verses 1 to 5).\nSymbolically, his age reduces to a 9,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15938359,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to indicate that this was a period of\ntime in which a spiritual cycle had  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15941840,
    "dDurationMs": 5800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "been completed. The addition of the\nHebrew Heh (H) to Abram’s name carries  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15947640,
    "dDurationMs": 5040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a 9 vibration as well.\nNew Testament.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15952680,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In the first 4 books of the New \nTestament, Matthew, Mark, Luke and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15956640,
    "dDurationMs": 4360,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "John, the writers express their Christian \nteachings mostly by allegory and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15961000,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "parable. These are meant to be interpreted \nin various ways; some apply to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15966000,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the cosmic world as a whole, some to \nour solar system, some to the entire\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15970680,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "human race and some to individuals. \nSince a person is called the microcosm\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15975520,
    "dDurationMs": 5480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "within the macrocosm, an individual \nrepresents, in miniature, all that is, was\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15981000,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and will be.\nAs in the Old Testament,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15984000,
    "dDurationMs": 5960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symbology is used also to point out significant\nhidden meanings in names and numbers. The art  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15989960,
    "dDurationMs": 2960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and science of numerology\nis one of the most obvious  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15992920,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "methods employed, although a deep\nunderstanding of the basic meanings of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 15996720,
    "dDurationMs": 4399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "numbers is necessary for a complete\nunravelling of inner meanings.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16001119,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The New Testament describes the path \nof faith. Faith is the conscious\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16005600,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "acceptance of wisdom and love. When \nfaith is strong the mind is at peace\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16010359,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the body is free of tension. Faith \nis a mystical conviction that God is\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16014760,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "presently a power within the individual. \nThe instinct to believe is as strong\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16019560,
    "dDurationMs": 4200,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as the instinct to survive, impelling one \nto search for a philosophy to sustain\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16023760,
    "dDurationMs": 4479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "one’s hopes and desires on the journey \nthrough life. It is said that primitive\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16028239,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "people were mystics by instinct, and \nthat modem people are mystics by\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16032239,
    "dDurationMs": 1480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "intuition.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16033720,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In Christian teachings Christ is the \nrevelation of the love and forgiveness\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16037640,
    "dDurationMs": 5960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of God. The Sermon on the Mount (Matthew \n5 verse 17) is the code of mystic\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16043600,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Christianity, and it is in the faithful \nheart that the Sermon is understood.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16049000,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The 12 disciples of Jesus represent \nan extension of the twelve tribes\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16053040,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of Israel. The 72 other disciples \ncorrespond to the six elders\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16057760,
    "dDurationMs": 6399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "chosen from each of the original 12 tribes.\nThe Pythagorean dodecahedron (a twelve-sided  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16064159,
    "dDurationMs": 2080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symmetrical figure\nwhich can be compared to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16066239,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the 12 lines of the Divine Triangle)\nrepresents the universe as related to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16071119,
    "dDurationMs": 4521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "humanity. This indicates that the\nindividual has within himself the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16075640,
    "dDurationMs": 3720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "potential of the 12 powers as they\nrelate to the inherent attributes  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16079359,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "within the 12 signs of the zodiac. The\nsearch for knowledge is motivated by the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16084359,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "desire to understand the self in\nrelation to God.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16088760,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The New Testament writers symbolically \napplied all the basic numbers to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16092720,
    "dDurationMs": 4399,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "express their ideas, but made more \nreferences to specific numbers relating\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16097119,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the seven-fold human body, to the \ndivine potential of the human mind\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16101439,
    "dDurationMs": 5641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and soul and to spiritual destiny. Many \nyears elapsed between the writing of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16107080,
    "dDurationMs": 3560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the Old and New Testaments which \nallowed time for much expansion of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16110640,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "human consciousness. As a result, \nmany more meanings for the numbers\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16115040,
    "dDurationMs": 4640,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "had accrued. The use of symbolism \nhad grown and was liberally employed\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16119680,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as a means of revelation.\n1 IS THE ZERO made more manifest;  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16124359,
    "dDurationMs": 5120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it is the self, independence and\nunity. In the beginning was the Word;  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16129479,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and the Word was God (John\n1 verse 1). 1 is the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16133239,
    "dDurationMs": 6120,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "basis or cause of a beginning; \nit is a start, a creative idea for expression.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16139359,
    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "2 ENCOMPASSES ALL PAIRS of \nopposites: male and female, spirit\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16144319,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and matter, heaven and hell. No \nman can serve two masters; ye\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16149479,
    "dDurationMs": 5720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "cannot serve God and Mammon (Matthew \n6 verse 24). There is always a choice\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16155199,
    "dDurationMs": 3721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be made between the pairs of \nopposites; thus we are warned that in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16158920,
    "dDurationMs": 5439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "duality there is danger. A house \ndivided against itself shall not stand \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16164359,
    "dDurationMs": 7920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "(Matthew 12 verse 25). But, if two agree, \nit shall be done (Matthew 18 verse 19).\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16172279,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "3 SYMBOLIZES THE TRINITY, triad \nand trine; the 3 dimensions.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16177119,
    "dDurationMs": 3801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In a larger sense, the 3 stands \nfor multiplication and growth.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16180920,
    "dDurationMs": 3800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Three of the disciples went with \nJesus into the garden of Gethsemane.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16184720,
    "dDurationMs": 6840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They were Peter, James and John; these \n3 stand for light, life and love.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16191560,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And Jesus went apart and prayed 3 \ntimes... each time He returned to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16195479,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "find them asleep. The inner meaning is \nthat Jesus felt that light, life and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16200359,
    "dDurationMs": 5561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "love were forsaking Him, as He said in \nHis prayer: Father, let this cup pass\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16205920,
    "dDurationMs": 9920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from me; nevertheless, Thy will be done (Matthew \n26 verses 37 to 45; Mark 14 verses 32 to 41).\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16215840,
    "dDurationMs": 6920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Jesus asked Peter 3 times: Lovest thou \nme? (John 21 verses 15 to 17). The\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16222760,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "three inquiries refer to love on \nthe 3 planes of consciousness - the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16226680,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "conscious mind, the subconscious mind \nand the super-conscious mind. If\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16231399,
    "dDurationMs": 4521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "two or three are gathered together in \nmy name, there am I in the midst of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16235920,
    "dDurationMs": 5359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "them (Matthew 18 verse 20). This also \nrefers to the 3 parts of the mind, \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16241279,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "declaring that if all agree, \nthe Christ power will prevail.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16245520,
    "dDurationMs": 5561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The story of Jesus is a story of \n3’s. He rose after 3 days and he was\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16251080,
    "dDurationMs": 4560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "denied thrice by Peter. The fact \nthat Jesus was crucified between two\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16255640,
    "dDurationMs": 4280,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "thieves is symbolic of the divided \nsystem of belief which has stolen many\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16259920,
    "dDurationMs": 4880,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the true teachings. Christ sat down \nwith the twelve, a higher vibration of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16264800,
    "dDurationMs": 5800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "3. Judas bargained for 30 pieces \nof silver, again a vibration of 3.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16270600,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "4 STANDS FOR LAW and order, \nmeasurement, the physical and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16274359,
    "dDurationMs": 4960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "material realms, reason, logic, the \nsquare and the cross. Whenever a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16279319,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number is made up of straight lines, \nit symbolizes the divine principle;\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16283560,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "therefore the 4 and the 7 are called \nsacred numbers. The symbols are the \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16287880,
    "dDurationMs": 5560,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "square and the cross. The cross is \nalways a sacred symbol wherever found.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16293439,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Traditionally, the equal-armed cross \nrepresented man. With the coming of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16298359,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Christ, the horizontal line of the cross \nwas raised from the umbilical center\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16302399,
    "dDurationMs": 5400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to the heart center. It is not necessarily \na Christian symbol; other spiritual\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16307800,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "leaders have died on the cross such \nas Krishna of India, Thamus of Syria,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16312319,
    "dDurationMs": 5561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Hesus of the Druids, Mithra of \nPersia and Quexalcotl of Mexico.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16317880,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "And He was there in the wilderness \nforty days tempted by Satan; and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16322040,
    "dDurationMs": 7359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "was with the wild beasts, and the angels \nministered unto him (Mark 1 verse 13).\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16329399,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "40 is used in a Scripture to indicate a \ncompleted cycle of retreat from things\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16333880,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the world in preparation for \nsomething better to follow.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16338159,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "On the morning of the fourth day after \nhe died, Lazarus (meaning lack of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16342239,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spiritual understanding) lay in the \ntomb, bound hand and foot, with grave\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16346800,
    "dDurationMs": 4800,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "clothes wound around him. The fourth \ndawning day is when spiritual\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16351600,
    "dDurationMs": 3440,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "understanding shall release us from \nthe grave of materialism and bring\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16355040,
    "dDurationMs": 4199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "awakening to the one light.\nAt the fourth watch, just as gray  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16359239,
    "dDurationMs": 4040,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "dawn was breaking, they beheld one\nwalking on the water (Matthew  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16363279,
    "dDurationMs": 8320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "14 verse 25). This refers metaphorically to the\ndawning of Aquarian Age, the age of community.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16371600,
    "dDurationMs": 4720,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "5 STANDS FOR MEDIATION, \nunderstanding and judgment. The\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16376319,
    "dDurationMs": 3960,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "ancients represented the world by \nthe number 5, the explanation being\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16380279,
    "dDurationMs": 6359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that in 5 are represented the four elements \nearth, water, fire and air, plus the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16386639,
    "dDurationMs": 6041,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "fifth essence, ether or spirit. Five \nbecame the number of humanity with the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16392680,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "five developed senses. It is the great \nwork of human beings to gain control\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16397520,
    "dDurationMs": 5961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "over the five senses, after which \nthe sixth sense, intuition develops.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16403480,
    "dDurationMs": 3559,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The five wounds of Christ symbolize \nthe suffering endured while in the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16407039,
    "dDurationMs": 5760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "flesh, which leads us to turn to God. \nIn the parable of the five wise and the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16412799,
    "dDurationMs": 5361,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "five foolish virgins (Matthew 25 verse \n3), they that were foolish took their\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16418160,
    "dDurationMs": 4959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lamps and took no oil with them. But \nthe wise took oil in their vessels with\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16423119,
    "dDurationMs": 5721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "their lamps. The oil relates to the \nanointed, or those who had light.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16428840,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Human beings can choose the light \nor reject it by their actions.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16433080,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Interestingly, the word oil is a \n9-powered word which means a completed\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16437760,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "cycle of attainment.\n6 IS THE NUMBER OF BALANCE,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16442320,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "harmony, cooperation, marriage,\nconnubiality and beauty. And  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16447240,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there were set there 6 water pots of\nstone (John 2 verse 6) for the wedding  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16451840,
    "dDurationMs": 5680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "feast. A wedding represents love (as does \nthe number 6) at its most blissful state  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16457520,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in earthly consciousness. The 6\nexpresses universal love, for out of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16462840,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the sorrows of personal love, the soul\nawakens to the higher life which leads  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16467080,
    "dDurationMs": 7879,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to illumination or adept ship. Jesus’s\nfirst miracle changed six pots of water to wine.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16474959,
    "dDurationMs": 6041,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "7 IS THE NUMBER OF REST, cessation \nbut not ceasing, safety, and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16481000,
    "dDurationMs": 6320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the full measure of the triad and the quaternary.\nOne of the greatest heritages from the Christian  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16487320,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Scriptures is the sevenfold \npath of the Lord’s prayer.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16491920,
    "dDurationMs": 6199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The seven statements express the triad and\nthe quaternary (Matthew 6 verses 9 to 13):\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16498119,
    "dDurationMs": 5361,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "1. Our Father which art in heaven,\n2. Hallowed be Thy Name.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16503480,
    "dDurationMs": 6000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "3. Thy kingdom come, Thy will be \ndone, on earth as it is in heaven.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16509480,
    "dDurationMs": 4799,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "4. Give us this day our daily bread, and\n5. Forgive us our debts as  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16514279,
    "dDurationMs": 4281,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we forgive our debtors.\n6. Lead us not into temptation,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16518561,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "7. But deliver us from evil.\nThe final statement (“For Thine  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16523080,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is the kingdom, and the power and the\nglory, forever”) was added much later to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16527561,
    "dDurationMs": 4039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symbolize return to the heavenly\nstate.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16531600,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "8 STANDS FOR INVOLUTION AND \nEVOLUTION, for cycles of ebb\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16535359,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and flow, infinity, rhythm, \nadvancement, strength and confidence.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16539799,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The 8 is not a primary number in the \nNew Testament. Rather, we find the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16544520,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "8 figures heavily in the eight-fold \npath of the Buddha and in occult\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16548799,
    "dDurationMs": 3441,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "literature.\n9 REFERS TO COMPLETION,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16552240,
    "dDurationMs": 5398,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "attainment, fulfillment, regeneration\nand revelation. Many words in the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16557639,
    "dDurationMs": 3160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Bible are used for their symbolic\nmeanings and teachings mystically  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16560799,
    "dDurationMs": 6801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "concealed. Bread and wine are usually\nlinked together. Bread is a 3-powered word;  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16567600,
    "dDurationMs": 3439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "wine is a 6-powered word;\ntogether they form a symbol  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16571039,
    "dDurationMs": 5801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of the 9-power of regeneration. Thus the\nserving of bread and wine means that one  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16576840,
    "dDurationMs": 4119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is to partake of a regenerative\nprocess when taking communion.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16580959,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In the Book of Revelation there are \ntwo numbers whose meanings have\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16584199,
    "dDurationMs": 7400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "caused much discussion. These two \nnumbers, the 666 and the 144,000 both\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16591600,
    "dDurationMs": 5359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vibrate to a 9. The 144,000 who were \nsealed as members of the Tribes of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16596959,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Israel refers to developed or saved \nhumanity. The seal refers to the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16601680,
    "dDurationMs": 6520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "protective sign in their foreheads \n(Revelations 9 verse 4). The 666, described\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16608199,
    "dDurationMs": 5201,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as the number of the beast (Revelations \n13 verse 18), refers to humanity\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16613400,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "functioning at the materialistic \nunregenerated level. Thus these two\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16618400,
    "dDurationMs": 6359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "numbers mystically refer to the evolution \nof humanity, either as lost (666)\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16624760,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or saved (144,000).\nHumanity, symbolically called  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16629920,
    "dDurationMs": 6119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the hand of God, demonstrates the same\nprinciple. Hand is a 9-powered word  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16636039,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and refers to humanity as one of God’s\nhelpers in bringing forth His Kingdom.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16640920,
    "dDurationMs": 3080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The nine statements of blessing in \nthe Sermon on the Mount, which show\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16644000,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a completed cycle, represent the \nessence of the New Testament teaching\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16648080,
    "dDurationMs": 6000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that the greatest of all power is love. \nLove is a 9-powered word. He that\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16654080,
    "dDurationMs": 6559,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "loveth not knoweth not God, for God is \nlove (First John 4 verse 8). God is love,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16660639,
    "dDurationMs": 4674,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and he that dwelleth in love, dwelleth \nin God, and God in him (First John\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16665312,
    "dDurationMs": 6207,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "4 verse 16). In the ninth hour - the hour \nof prayer - Christ on the cross said,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16671520,
    "dDurationMs": 6160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "“It is finished” (John 19 verse 30).\nThe numbers 12 and 13 hold a special place  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16677680,
    "dDurationMs": 2680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in both the Old and New\nTestaments.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16680359,
    "dDurationMs": 5641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "12. THERE WERE 12 Tribes of Israel \nwho were the sons of Jacob.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16686000,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When Jacob gave his blessing to his \ntwelve sons, he was referring not only\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16690000,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to twelve individuals, but to the \ndevelopment of 12 attributes to be\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16694279,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "awakened in the human soul. These \nparalleled the 12 characteristics of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16698719,
    "dDurationMs": 6961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the 12 signs of the zodiac (Genesis 49 \nverses 1 to 28). The work of these 12\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16705680,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sons dominated most of the Old \nTestament. Each tribe expressed the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16709920,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "qualities of one sign of the zodiac \nand responded to a certain number. No\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16714920,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "tribe was wholly good or bad. These \n12 signs and their corresponding\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16719520,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "numbers are operative in the lives \nof every individual, for each person\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16723439,
    "dDurationMs": 2600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "indeed is a miniature universe.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16726039,
    "dDurationMs": 4641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Jesus chose to have twelve apostles. \nThese also relate in character to the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16730680,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "twelve signs of the zodiac to make a \ncomplete gathering of types of people\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16734600,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the inner circle of followers of Jesus. \nThus the vibrational force under the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16739520,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number 12 belongs to the developed \nsoul who has accumulated unusual\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16743959,
    "dDurationMs": 3721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "inner strength through many \nand varied experiences.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16747680,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "13 IS A NUMBER of special significance. \nNote that there were twelve\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16752400,
    "dDurationMs": 5359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "apostles, but Jesus, the Christ, made a \nthirteenth member at the last supper.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16757760,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "12 is the number of solar months in the \nyear, but 13 is the number of lunar\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16762039,
    "dDurationMs": 5041,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "months. While the solar vibrations are \npositive and creative in type, the lunar\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16767080,
    "dDurationMs": 5039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vibrations are negative and receptive in type. \nEach, as a reflection of God,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16772119,
    "dDurationMs": 3320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is equally important.\n13 means either death  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16775439,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through degeneration, or life and attainment\nthrough regeneration. There are no halfway  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16780680,
    "dDurationMs": 5039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "measures in 13; it requires all\nor nothing. If 13 is your number,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16785719,
    "dDurationMs": 2801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "face it and win!\n“Choose ye this day whom  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16788520,
    "dDurationMs": 6801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "ye will serve” (Joshua 24 verse 15). In\nDeuteronomy 30 verse 16, Moses said:  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16795320,
    "dDurationMs": 5639,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "“See, I have set before thee this day life\nand good - or death and evil - therefore choose  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16800959,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "life, and both thou and thy\nseed shall live.”\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16804719,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Incarnation in the flesh represents \nthe soul’s burial in matter, where it\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16809279,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "loses the power it originally had in \nthe ethereal realm where it was created\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16813199,
    "dDurationMs": 4201,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to be a companion to God. Eating of \nthe Tree of Knowledge of Good and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16817400,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Evil leads to spiritual, not physical, \ndeath. When the soul turns from God to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16822480,
    "dDurationMs": 5799,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "self it figuratively dies. We wander \nabout on earth in the flesh, as prodigal\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16828279,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "sons and daughters, victims of spiritual \namnesia. The prodigal, even as you\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16833520,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and I, went from the father’s home of \nhis own free will; the father did not\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16838359,
    "dDurationMs": 3160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "send him.\nBoth the Old and the New  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16841520,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Testaments contain numerous instances of the\nuse of numerological symbols in the form of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16846240,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "parable and allegory. Because\nevery number and letter has  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16850320,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a dual meaning, hidden messages are\ndiscernible to readers who understand the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16854561,
    "dDurationMs": 3398,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "number-letter codes employed in\nbiblical times.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16857959,
    "dDurationMs": 3000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "In addition, there are 3 levels \nof meaning or knowledge which the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16860959,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "reader can acquire. The first level \ncomes through the conscious mind and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16865359,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "applies to the material or physical \nworld. The second level is absorbed\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16869840,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through the subconscious mind and is \nacquired by means of parables and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16873359,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symbols. The third level deals with \nrevelations on the super-conscious plane\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16878080,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of thought and affirms that we must \nrediscover who we are from within.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16883240,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Bible is the story of humanity \nand its generations (growth and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16887400,
    "dDurationMs": 4559,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "attainment), of its degeneration (the \nprodigal who left his father’s house\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16891959,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "forgetful of his divinity) and of its \nregeneration through the possible path of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16896359,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "return to the consciousness within \nwhich proclaims: “Thy Will be done.”\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16902119,
    "dDurationMs": 4240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "PART 2: DOUBLE-DIGIT DELINEATIONS.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16906359,
    "dDurationMs": 2600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "YOUR WAY OF SUCCESS and \nhappiness is hidden in your name\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16908959,
    "dDurationMs": 3441,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and birthdate, as well as the ways \nto overcome the difficulties found\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16912400,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "there. These paths must be hunted \nout, understood and explained when\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16916400,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "analyzing a number chart, because \nthe way to overcome obstacles lies\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16920680,
    "dDurationMs": 4801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "alongside the indicators of success and \nhappiness. It is always a question of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16925480,
    "dDurationMs": 4479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "action and reaction, whether the positive \nor the negative choice is taken.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16929959,
    "dDurationMs": 4121,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "When you understand that you have \nchoices, and you know what they are,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16934080,
    "dDurationMs": 3719,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can conduct your life in such a \nway as to attain any goal you set for\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16937799,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "yourself. It is important that you \nchoose a goal and then examine the way\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16942879,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "your cosmic gifts have prepared \nyou for its achievement.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16946359,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The meanings of the single digits are \nexplicit; when the single digits are\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16950680,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "combined to form the double digits, \nthey provide a more complete picture\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16954600,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of how you will express your talents. \nThe double digits show patterns of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16959199,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "experience; they indicate destiny and \npoint the way to success. These facets\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16964719,
    "dDurationMs": 3441,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of your character cannot be discovered \nin detail except by careful\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16968160,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "consideration of the double numbers \nproduced by your name and birthdate.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16972561,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "This is primarily a book on numerology, \nbut since we use the double\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16976080,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "digits up through 78, which is the number \nof cards in the Tarot deck, we are\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16980680,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "including brief excerpts of the Tarot \nphilosophy as a further dimension in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16985199,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "understanding the numbers. The Tarot \nkeys symbolize ways of determining\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16989760,
    "dDurationMs": 3680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the strengths and weaknesses \nof dynamic life forces.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16993439,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Rich in symbolism, the Tarot has \nfrom ancient times been used to help\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 16997439,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "people understand the laws of the \nuniverse and our relation to these laws.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17002199,
    "dDurationMs": 4641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The 22 keys of the Major Arcana \nrelate a story of our lives, of how\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17006840,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "we are constituted and what our \npossibilities are. If we all studied and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17011680,
    "dDurationMs": 3840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "followed these laws, our lives would \nimprove in consciousness and inner\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17015520,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "security. The 56 minor keys explain \nthe many phases of human life\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17020760,
    "dDurationMs": 3199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and symbolize ways to face our dilemmas.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17023959,
    "dDurationMs": 3961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Tarot also relates to areas of the \nzodiac, and for those students who\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17027920,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "wish to plumb the depths of astrology, \nwe have included in the delineations\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17032080,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the astrological assignments for \neach of the 78 numbers. In fact,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17036760,
    "dDurationMs": 4641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the sciences of numerology, astrology \nand the Tarot coincide and confirm\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17041400,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "each other so perfectly that we have \nfound it almost impossible to analyze a\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17045680,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "chart of any kind without somehow \nincluding concepts from each science to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17050561,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "enhance our understanding of the chart. \nIn their most exalted use, these\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17055480,
    "dDurationMs": 3119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "three sciences will synthesize the \nknowledge contained in their rich\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17058600,
    "dDurationMs": 4080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "symbolism, so that we may apply it in \nour lives toward understanding our\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17062680,
    "dDurationMs": 5199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "relationship with God.\nHow to Read Your Number.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17067879,
    "dDurationMs": 4801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Suppose your number is 32 or 5: read \nthe delineation for the double number\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17072680,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "first, then read the delineation for the \nsingle digit that it reduces to. Keep in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17077840,
    "dDurationMs": 4641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "mind that it is the 2 working through \nthe 3 to achieve the base number 5,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17082480,
    "dDurationMs": 6520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "which is synthesized in the 32 or 5 delineation. \nA 41 or 5 is an entirely different 5\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17089000,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vibration, with a 1 working through \na 4 to achieve the base number 5.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17094160,
    "dDurationMs": 3439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "A number always has the same meaning, \nno matter where it appears in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17097600,
    "dDurationMs": 3961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "your chart, but the expression of its \nconsciousness is determined by its\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17101561,
    "dDurationMs": 5479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "position as your Soul, Outer Personality, \nPath of Destiny or Life Lesson\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 17107039,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Number. Therefore it is important \nto consider where the number is\n "
