  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20467799,
    "dDurationMs": 3121,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and become masters.\nYou are a perceptive  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20470920,
    "dDurationMs": 5039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "person who understands human nature. When you\nmeet someone you are not often fooled by their  "
