    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the outer world drives\nyou to a lonely existence,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20581279,
    "dDurationMs": 6240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "where you become a hermit or recluse, and shut\nout the people who cannot live up to your ideals.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20587520,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "However, by using your will and by \ngaining control of your tremendous\n "
    } ]
  }, {
