    "tStartMs": 20595320,
    "dDurationMs": 4840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "needs what you have to offer: \na sound creative mind.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20600160,
    "dDurationMs": 7039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "7 AS A TEMPORARY VIBRATION: Reflection, \nrest, health, vacations. It\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20607199,
    "dDurationMs": 5439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is time to rest; God rested on the seventh \nday, and this is your seventh day.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20612639,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Become quiet and receptive. Think about \nyourself and your station in life.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20618000,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Analyze your goals, projects and \nrelationships. Spend time by yourself and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20622439,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "listen to your inner promptings. \nWrite down your thoughts. You can be\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20627160,
    "dDurationMs": 4119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "inspired by dreams, visions, and intuitions now;  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20631279,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "therefore, any writings you\nproduce can be creatively moving.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20635559,
    "dDurationMs": 4561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Use the energies of this period for \nmental exercise and discipline. Now\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20640119,
    "dDurationMs": 4121,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can master technical skills to aid \nin your profession, or benefit from\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20644240,
    "dDurationMs": 4318,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "philosophical and metaphysical \ndisciplines including religion, yoga,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20648559,
    "dDurationMs": 4842,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "transcendental meditation, \nastrology and numerology.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20653400,
    "dDurationMs": 4318,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Do not push your financial affairs \nunder a 7. This is not a time to be\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20657719,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "impulsive or concern yourself with \nbusiness. It is a time of physical\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20661719,
    "dDurationMs": 3240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "completion and attainment in the \ncycles because you can see the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20664959,
    "dDurationMs": 4281,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "consequences of your previous efforts.\nMatters mysteriously complete themselves  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20669240,
    "dDurationMs": 5199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "without any effort on your part. \nWait and let the cycle work for you.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20674439,
    "dDurationMs": 3961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The number 7 rules the physical body \nand body functions; therefore, the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20678400,
    "dDurationMs": 4799,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "forces within your body are now active. \nYou must pace yourself wisely, rest\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20683199,
    "dDurationMs": 4961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and take care of minor problems. \nAbuse and overexertion can bring on\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20688160,
    "dDurationMs": 5240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "physical maladies and illnesses. These \ndiscomforts force you to slow down,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20693400,
    "dDurationMs": 3439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so that you will take the time to reflect \nupon yourself and your purpose in \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20696840,
    "dDurationMs": 5600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "life, which is the most important reason \nfor this cycle. Vacations are always\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20702439,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "pleasant, and now is a good time to take one.\nBe careful when signing any documents  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20707959,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or legal agreements. Check\nevery word and look for loopholes;  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20712279,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when you have thoroughly scrutinized\nall aspects, sign with confidence.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20717160,
    "dDurationMs": 4559,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You will not feel the need to socialize \nat this time; rather, you prefer\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20721719,
    "dDurationMs": 4521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "either to be alone or to be with people \nof a spiritual nature who complement\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20726240,
    "dDurationMs": 5398,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and uplift your contemplative mood. Do \nnot fight your inner urgings to rest,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20731639,
    "dDurationMs": 5602,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for that will only bring on physical \nproblems and frustration. Instead, flow\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20737240,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with this and look deep within yourself \nto discover the beautiful facets of\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20741400,
    "dDurationMs": 8199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "your true inner self, the perfect jewel.\nTAROT SYMBOLISM: Key 7. The Chariot.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20749600,
    "dDurationMs": 2721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The Chariot represents\nreceptivity to the will of the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20752320,
    "dDurationMs": 6000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "one Source. The keyword attributed to this card\nis fence or enclosure, and its sense function is  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20758320,
    "dDurationMs": 3879,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "speech. Every word we speak\nis a fence enclosing an idea  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20762199,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or thought. An eloquent vocabulary is a\npowerful tool for protection and preservation,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20767719,
    "dDurationMs": 3080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "as well as advancement.\nWhen we speak we set in motion  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20770799,
    "dDurationMs": 6641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a vibration that acts upon the ethers, space\nand akasha. Blavatsky said, “Sound or speech  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20777439,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "is a tremendous force when\ndirected by occult knowledge.”  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20780959,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It is only when we become still, quiet and\nreceptive that we can be victorious. Then the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20787039,
    "dDurationMs": 2680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "primal force can work through\nus.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20789719,
    "dDurationMs": 6400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Symbolically, the Charioteer is the \nsoul, directing the chariot, the body.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20796119,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Notice that the Charioteer has no reins. \nIt is mentally, through the will, that\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 20801279,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "he directs the sphinxes, the positive \nand negative senses, to draw the chariot\n "
