      "utf8": "Number 8 individuals have the capacity \nfor the top executive positions.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21335479,
    "dDurationMs": 3602,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "They possess enormous reserves of \nstrength, which can be called upon\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21339080,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "when the pressure is heavy. Many \noutstanding athletes also have an 8 in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21343680,
    "dDurationMs": 6160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "their personal expression.\n9 AS A PERSONAL NUMBER  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21349840,
    "dDurationMs": 5680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "VIBRATION: You are a humanitarian,\na universalist who thinks in abstract  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21355520,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "terms. Born for service to others,\nyou want to make the world a better  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21360279,
    "dDurationMs": 6160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "place in which to live. Since 9 is the\nlast single digit, it indicates attainment,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21366439,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "perfection and completion, the\nseeds for new beginnings, the foundation  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21371199,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for future growth in the next or\nhigher cycle.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21374680,
    "dDurationMs": 3119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You have a thirst for spiritual \nknowledge and an urge for freedom and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21377799,
    "dDurationMs": 5521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "wisdom that transcends personal needs. \nYou desire to live an ideal life\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21383320,
    "dDurationMs": 4039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "according to your inspirations and \naspirations. Through your responsive\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21387359,
    "dDurationMs": 3801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "reaching out to the world, you \nbecome a beacon for others.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21391160,
    "dDurationMs": 4359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "The number 9 is a testing number. \nThe higher you evolve, the more\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21395520,
    "dDurationMs": 4641,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "difficulties you may encounter. You \nshould be tolerant of and merciful to\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21400160,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "others on your path. In this way you \nwill be an example for them, and they\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21404920,
    "dDurationMs": 4039,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "will recognize your sympathetic and \ncompassionate nature. People will be\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21408959,
    "dDurationMs": 3480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "drawn to you for your deep \nand broad understanding.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21412439,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Your thinking is vast, and without \nlimits. Because of your openness, your\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21417119,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "psychic abilities are well developed, \nand foresight, premonitions and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21421279,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "predictions flow from you with ease. \nYou seem to have a direct line to the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21425559,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "mysteries of life. You have very \nstrong emotions and feelings and could\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21430439,
    "dDurationMs": 5561,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "evolve a new philosophy for humanity.\nYou are generous and idealistic. For  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21436000,
    "dDurationMs": 3680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "anyone who needs your wisdom and\nguidance, you are open-handed and  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21439680,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "beneficent, because you realize that\nknowledge belongs to those who seek it.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21444840,
    "dDurationMs": 3639,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Charitable work is close to your\nheart, and you are likely to be  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21448479,
    "dDurationMs": 4201,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "a patron of the arts and sciences.\nYour associations with other people  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21452680,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in your life are intense, but not\nnecessarily enduring. You must learn  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21457359,
    "dDurationMs": 4000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "to let friends go when their needs have\nbeen filled, because your destiny is to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21461359,
    "dDurationMs": 5439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "be a loner, a sort of recluse. You are\nnot meant to sit alone meditating on a  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21466799,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "mountaintop, but your innate wisdom\nand understanding separate you from  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21471279,
    "dDurationMs": 4600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the crowd. You must share your\nwisdom to enlighten the world,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21475879,
    "dDurationMs": 4961,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so you cannot be bound by enduring ties\nthat would limit your mobility.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21480840,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Your life cycle includes travel and\nassociations with famous personalities  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21484760,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who will be drawn to you by your \nfree spirit and broad compassion.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21488680,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Your friendship encompasses the world.\nYou easily acquire money and independence,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21493760,
    "dDurationMs": 3400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "so that you are free to pursue\nyour worldly destiny.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21497160,
    "dDurationMs": 3479,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "If you are a negative 9, you are \nself-serving and concerned with your\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21500639,
    "dDurationMs": 4441,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "own needs rather than the needs of \nothers. This self-indulgence precludes\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21505080,
    "dDurationMs": 5119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "belief in a higher source and can result \nin faithlessness. When crossed you\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21510199,
    "dDurationMs": 6121,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are quick tempered. Your keen mind \nmakes you a formidable enemy. Since\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21516320,
    "dDurationMs": 3920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "9’s have to live up to a higher standard \nthan the other numbers, the resulting\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21520240,
    "dDurationMs": 4318,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "tension can cause nervous troubles. \nThis can produce unhappy relations\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21524559,
    "dDurationMs": 4441,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "with others, including your mate.\nCorinne Heline says in The Sacred  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21529000,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Science of Numbers: “The 9\nindividual has run the gamut  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21532760,
    "dDurationMs": 6080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of personal experiences, including both the\nhigh and the low, the mundane and the spiritual.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21538840,
    "dDurationMs": 3080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "It is the synthesis of these\nexperiences which produces  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21541920,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "that sympathy, compassion and rare\nunderstanding which is characteristic of the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21546240,
    "dDurationMs": 3959,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "9.” Using the enhancing\nqualities of your number 9,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21550199,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you can be the visionary for whom all things are\npossible. Your faith in life embraces all and  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21555520,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "looks forward to evolution as\nthe promise of the spirit.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21559680,
    "dDurationMs": 5760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "9 AS A TEMPORARY VIBRATION: \nChanges, endings, charity,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21565439,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "inspiration. Events take place quickly \nat this time, with many stops and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21570119,
    "dDurationMs": 5000,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "starts, because you are experiencing \na period of change and transition. As\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21575119,
    "dDurationMs": 4121,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Paul Case says in The Tarot, “You \nmust make the final selection between\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21579240,
    "dDurationMs": 6160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "assimilable material and what is rejected \nas waste.” Eliminating the useless,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21585400,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and separating yourself from past \nmistakes can be an emotional experience,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21589840,
    "dDurationMs": 4719,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "for we often are reluctant to let go \nof the obstacles in our lives. If you\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21594559,
    "dDurationMs": 3721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "cannot free yourself from associations \nand situations that are no longer\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21598279,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "necessary for your development, then \nthe 9 cycle will do it for you. A\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21603600,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "vacation or trip would be good therapy \nat this time, giving you time to think\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21608320,
    "dDurationMs": 3318,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and separate yourself from the \nemotionalism you might encounter under\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21611639,
    "dDurationMs": 3160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this vibration.\nMany of your goals will be  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21614799,
    "dDurationMs": 4201,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "realized during this time, and you should\nattempt to finish all projects that  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21619000,
    "dDurationMs": 6359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "are close to completion. As this is an\nending cycle, do not make new commitments.  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21625359,
    "dDurationMs": 3199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Projects begun under a 9\nhave little durability.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21628559,
    "dDurationMs": 3320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Present friendships can be cemented \nand made more enduring, and you\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21631879,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "may receive gifts from friends. This \nshould be a charitable time, in which \n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21636039,
    "dDurationMs": 4680,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "you think primarily of other people’s welfare.\nDo something for others in thanks for the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21640719,
    "dDurationMs": 3521,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "blessings you have received \nin this life. An old friend or  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21644240,
    "dDurationMs": 4199,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "lover may enter your life briefly \nfor one last encounter, but don’t  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21648439,
    "dDurationMs": 4760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "expect this sudden renewal to last.\nSince this is an ending cycle, you may  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21653199,
    "dDurationMs": 4480,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "change jobs or residence. Children\nmay leave home for higher education  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21657680,
    "dDurationMs": 4359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "or marriage, or to begin their own\nlives. If you are separated from the  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21662039,
    "dDurationMs": 5041,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "people, situations and locations with\nwhich you have lived for a long time,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21667080,
    "dDurationMs": 4639,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it is because they no longer serve\nyour evolutionary process.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21671719,
    "dDurationMs": 5441,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Use the creative powers of this vibration \nto develop your artistic abilities.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21677160,
    "dDurationMs": 5160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "You will have inspirational ideas that \ncan be used productively in the future\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21682320,
    "dDurationMs": 3439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in a way that the next cycle’s \nnumber will determine.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21685760,
    "dDurationMs": 5119,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Don’t be caught by your emotions. \nHanging on to the past, wallowing in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21690879,
    "dDurationMs": 5121,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "what used to be can only bring \ndiscontentment, frustration and depression.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21696000,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Rather, look forward with joy and high \nexpectations to the future, for which\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21701080,
    "dDurationMs": 4439,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the releasing energy of this cycle \nhas prepared you. Use the wisdom\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21705520,
    "dDurationMs": 3760,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "provided by the events of this cycle to \ninspire your actions productively in\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21709279,
    "dDurationMs": 2240,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the future.\nTAROT SYMBOLISM:  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21711520,
    "dDurationMs": 5600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Key 9. The Hermit. The symbol for key 9 is the\nyod, the tongue of flame,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21717119,
    "dDurationMs": 5320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the glyph that makes up every letter in the\nHebrew alphabet. It represents the fiery energy,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21722439,
    "dDurationMs": 2840,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the life force, and the hand,\nopened rather than closed,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21725279,
    "dDurationMs": 5359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "of man and woman. In the body we are little\nserpents, containing a portion of the one  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21730639,
    "dDurationMs": 5682,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Source’s fiery energy. As such, we\nare the hands of God operating  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21736320,
    "dDurationMs": 3398,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "in the physical world.\nThe Hermit is a symbol of  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21739719,
    "dDurationMs": 6361,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "ageless wisdom, standing on the mountain of\nattainment. He has achieved. The snow  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21746080,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "represents the isolation he endures\nbecause his wisdom sets him apart  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21749600,
    "dDurationMs": 5879,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "from others. However, as he turns to\nshine his light on those who follow him,  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21755479,
    "dDurationMs": 4041,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "he intimates that our knowledge is\nempty and meaningless until we turn  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21759520,
    "dDurationMs": 5520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and give it to others. The Hermit has\nevaluated, selecting the necessary and  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21765039,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "discarding the unnecessary elements\nalong his path. He has learned to  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21769359,
    "dDurationMs": 4920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "use the Magician’s wand, which he now\nleans on, for he knows he can depend upon  "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21774279,
    "dDurationMs": 4279,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "it for support. He has achieved\nmastery.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21778559,
    "dDurationMs": 5041,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "ASTROLOGICAL CORRESPONDENCE: \nSun (and Virgo). The Sun is\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21783600,
    "dDurationMs": 3520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "assigned to 9 because it is only after \nyou carefully progress through the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21787119,
    "dDurationMs": 4160,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "previous steps, 1 through 8, that you \ncan attain a position of respect and\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21791279,
    "dDurationMs": 4721,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "leadership, as well as a full recognition \nof your inner potential. The true\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21796000,
    "dDurationMs": 5080,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "inner self is expressed under a 9, \nas you become the humanitarian, the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21801080,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "universalist who reaches out to the \nmultitudes to lighten their burdens\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21804680,
    "dDurationMs": 3600,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "through your understanding, \nwisdom and compassion.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21808279,
    "dDurationMs": 4400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "Virgo’s assignment indicates that \ncareful, thorough analysis has preceded\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21812680,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "this final position of authority. Any \nmistakes along the path could have led\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21817199,
    "dDurationMs": 7400,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "the aspirant astray; therefore, keen \ndiscrimination is necessary at all times.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21824600,
    "dDurationMs": 4801,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "10/1 AS A PERSONAL NUMBER \nVIBRATION: If you embrace the\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21829400,
    "dDurationMs": 3719,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "philosophy of reincarnation, you will \nrecognize that you are an old soul\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21833119,
    "dDurationMs": 4359,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "who has lived many lives of both high \nand low degree and who has learned\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21837479,
    "dDurationMs": 4881,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "how transitory the things of the earth \nare. You have a talent for influencing\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21842359,
    "dDurationMs": 4320,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "and bringing people together, and you \nare a power person who has a special\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21846680,
    "dDurationMs": 4520,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "spiritual mission in the world. Your \nword is power and your presence,\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 21851199,
