      "utf8": "can all be yours during this \npowerful material period.\n "
    } ]
  }, {
    "tStartMs": 26630639,
    "dDurationMs": 6920,
    "segs": [ {
      "utf8": "TAROT SYMBOLISM: Key 0; and 22). \nThe Fool (before and after). The\n "
